error[P065]: expression statement has no observable effect
  --> tests/parser/errors/expr_stmt_useless_ident.mochi:2:1

  2 | x
    | ^

help:
  An expression used as a statement must perform I/O or call a function. Bare values, arithmetic, and field/index access compute a result that nothing reads. Use `let _ = ...` if you need to evaluate for a side effect inside an argument, or remove the line.
